    "Here, we use a simpler and shorter ReAct prompt provided by Langchain foot_2.",
    "We present the ASR-valid results in Table 11 and ASR-all resuls in Table 12.",
    "To conduct a more detailed analysis, we present the heatmaps of the attack success rates across each test case in Figure 6.",
    "The success rates are calculated based on the performance of the prompted agents, and we only consider the direct harm attacks for simplicity.",
    "We also compare different experiment configurations with long and short prompts under base and enhanced settings."
